item.itunes:summary: A real estate video tour featuring 117 Crossfire Road, Holly Springs, NC 27540. 3 Bedrooms, 2 Bathrooms, MLS# 1658506. Gorgeous property located in one of the most desirable communities in Holly Springs, NC. The immaculate yard is fenced in the rear and has a large side yard. Inside, beautiful hardwood floors greet you at the door and flow all through the living and dining areas. Hardwood treads on the open staircase lead to the Master Suite. There is a niche and accent lights above the gas fireplace with marble hearth. The organized kitchen is open to the living and dining areas. Ceramic tile floors and kitchen backsplash are just some of the eye-catching features. The Master Suite is spacious and has a cathedral ceiling & palladium window. The Master Bath features a vaulted ceiling, double vanity, completely tiled shower and a garden tub with tile surround. Plenty of light shines through between the octagonal-shaped window and window above the garden tub. The walk in closet has lots of shelving and there is also a mirror-faced mini-armoire. Bedroom 1 features a cathedral ceiling, a palladium window and a plant ledge. You'll spend all your summer days in the backyard where the over-sized deck overlooks a yard that was obviously loved! This home is very convenient to shopping, restaurants, and 3/10 of a mile from the park, complete with running trails. It also just happens to be down the block from the communityâ€™s pool and playground. For more information, please contact Terri Perry by email at tperry999@earthlink.ney, or visit them online at www.McNamaraProperties.net today!
